results.name: Row sums of A268719: a(n) = Sum_{k=0..n} A003188(A006068(n)+A006068(k)).
link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..8191
program: (define (A268720 n) (add (lambda (k) (A268715bi n k)) 0 n)) ;; Code for A268715bi given in A268715.
(define (add intfun lowlim uplim) (let sumloop ((i lowlim) (res 0)) (cond ((> i uplim) res) (else (sumloop (1+ i) (+ res (intfun i)))))))
